# 3. MAPPER — RS material identity resolver
#    Ported/adapted from the proven EI injection identity-resolution architecture:
#    descriptor stripping, identity-source pooling, canonical tokens, brand/family
#    recognition, negative-pair protection, confidence scoring, and semantic
#    fallback. NONE of the EI element/PDE/Q3D calculation logic is reused — only
#    the identity-resolution framework.
# ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# Non-identity noise tokens removed from matching pools (Red Flag 2).
